divs: Sighting Detailsi was gong to lock my car up for the ight that was parked in the road. i got to the end of my driveway and looked a the night sky( i love looking at the stars).i looked up and saw what looked like a shooting star, so i paused to look, but i realized it wasnt because it didnt burn up like one. and on the leading tip was a rapid flashing light.i couldnt look away or move. it had to be super far up in the sky and it was traveling at a very fast speed. it travelled the whole night sky in atleast 5 seconds. much faster than a plane. its tail end looked like a shooting star, but i t couldnt have been because it was flashing. then it disapered as fast as it came.
